cution-1)ExecutiveAgenda+Objective(baselineforthisseries)">1) Executive Age=
nda + Objective (baseline for this series)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"6dd08da65000"><strong>Executive Agenda (30 minutes) =E2=80=
=94 Team Direction &amp; Execution (with Birger Fjaellman )</strong> <br><s=
trong>Objective:</strong> Align on direction, confirm execution path, and l=
eave with <strong>3=E2=80=935 explicit decisions/asks that unblock delivery=
