cution-2)The=E2=80=9Cdecision/ask=E2=80=9Dbacklogcarriedintheagendaemail">2=
) The =E2=80=9Cdecision/ask=E2=80=9D backlog carried in the agenda email</h=
3>
<p local-id=3D"d79ca20de6cc">These are the explicit items you listed as the=
 working queue:</p>
