<li local-id=3D"303d2072-45b6-4396-8f20-4a70c707847c">
<p local-id=3D"40cfa065f856">Jonan Tan Pangan + David Klan to co=E2=80=91de=
velop a <strong>prioritized checklist</strong> of services to transition (b=
iggest wins + unclear areas flagged). Lists created based on metal and # of=
 incidents/downtime</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"f8cdc781ff8c" id=3D"id-20260423-LapuLapuTeamDirectionandExe=
cution-4)Patching/orphanserverdetailseeninmeetingchat/messageartifact">4) P=
